    <h1>Gray Hat SEO</h1>
    <p class="description">SEO tactics that sit in the ambiguous space between Google-approved white hat methods and explicitly prohibited black hat techniques. Not currently banned — but ethically unclear, potentially risky, and subject to change as Google's guidelines evolve.</p>
    <div class="post-meta">
      <div class="meta-author">
        <div class="meta-avatar">AVR</div>
        <div class="meta-author-info">
          <span class="meta-author-name"><a href="/authors/akshay-vr/">Akshay VR</a></span>
